---
// Services Section Component
---

<section id="services" class="py-20 md:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-100 mb-4">
        Services
      </h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Strategic technology leadership for companies at critical inflection points.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Service Cards Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8">
      <!-- Service Card 1: AI Strategy & Governance -->
      <article class="group backdrop-blur-md bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-teal-500/50 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-teal-500/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-teal-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-teal-400 transition-colors">
          AI Strategy & Governance
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Navigate the AI landscape with confidence. Strategic guidance on LLM adoption, prompt engineering, security controls, and responsible AI implementation. Recent specializations from UPenn and Vanderbilt. Led enterprise-wide AI transformation initiatives, training teams on GitHub Copilot, autonomous agents, and context engineering best practices.
        </p>
      </article>
      
      <!-- Service Card 2: Security & Compliance Leadership -->
      <article class="group backdrop-blur-md bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-teal-500/50 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-teal-500/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-teal-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-teal-400 transition-colors">
          Security & Compliance Leadership
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          World-class security expertise with a proven 20-year zero-breach record. Deep experience in PCI-DSS, SOC audits, and regulatory compliance for FinTech and SaaS environments. Strategic oversight of security programs, risk management, policy development, and audit readiness. CISSP, CISA, CISM, CCSP certified.
        </p>
      </article>
      
      <!-- Service Card 3: Cloud & Infrastructure Transformation -->
      <article class="group backdrop-blur-md bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-teal-500/50 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-teal-500/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-teal-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 15a4 4 0 004 4h9a5 5 0 10-.1-9.999 5.002 5.002 0 10-9.78 2.096A4.001 4.001 0 003 15z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-teal-400 transition-colors">
          Cloud & Infrastructure Transformation
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Battle-tested infrastructure modernization expertise. Led comprehensive digital transformations from legacy bare-metal to 500+ VM hybrid-cloud environments. Expertise in Infrastructure as Code (Ansible), disaster recovery architecture, high-availability design (>99.99% uptime), and scaling SaaS operations through rapid growth and M&A integrations.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Additional Services Grid -->
    <div class="mt-16 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <!-- Additional Service 1 -->
      <article class="backdrop-blur-sm bg-slate-900/30 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-teal-500/30 transition-all duration-300">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100 mb-2">
          Fractional CTO Services
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400">
          Executive technology leadership on demand. Strategic planning, team development, vendor management, and technical architecture for growing companies.
        </p>
      </article>
      
      <!-- Additional Service 2 -->
      <article class="backdrop-blur-sm bg-slate-900/30 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-teal-500/30 transition-all duration-300">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100 mb-2">
          Technical Due Diligence
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400">
          M&A technical assessments for private equity and corporate acquirers. Infrastructure audits, security posture reviews, and integration planning.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
